marketing: Premium “universal tractor transmission oil” (UTTO) designed for use in transmissions, hydraulic systems, oil immersed brakes and other ancillary systems fitted to agricultural tractors and off-road equipment. Spirax S4 TXM-I is recognised by leading agricultural equipment manufacturers and suitable for use in most modern equipment.
